### Connect to XRPL Testnet
GET http://localhost:3000/api/connect


### Generate Wallet
POST http://localhost:3000/api/generate-wallet


### Mint NFT Ticket
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mint-ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seed": "sExampleSeed",
  "uri": "ipfs://example-uri"
}


### Extract invoice (OCR for JPEG/PNG, text layer for PDF)
# Put a sample invoice at ./samples/invoice.jpg (or .pdf) and run this.
POST http://localhost:3000/api/extract-invoice
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----TradeFlowBoundary

------TradeFlowBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="invoice.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/invoice.jpg
------TradeFlowBoundary--

